OL,3,CThree children and two adults injured
OL,4,Cin 'targeted' arson attack
OL,6,FFive people, including three children,
OL,7,Fare recovering after being injured in
OL,8,Fa "disturbing" arson attack.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FHalifax Road, in Rochdale, at 8:30pm
OL,12,Fon Wednesday, 4 September, after
OL,13,Freports of a fire.
OL,15,FThree children and two adults were
OL,16,Ftreated in hospital for their
OL,17,Finjuries, which officers say are not
OL,18,Flife-threatening or life-changing.
