OL,3,CThree children and two adults injured
OL,4,Cin 'targeted' arson attack
OL,6,FDetectives say that they think it
OL,7,Fcould have been a targeted arson
OL,8,Fattack, and they are appealing for
OL,9,Fwitnesses.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Katie Buntine
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is a disturbing incident
OL,13,Fwhere a property has been targeted,
OL,14,Fplacing a family and three young
OL,15,Fchildren at risk of serious harm.
OL,17,F"Our investigation is in the early
OL,18,Fstages, and we will remain at the
OL,19,Fscene today whilst we conduct further
OL,20,Fenquiries and to provide a visible
OL,21,Freassurance to the community.
