OL,6,F"We are appealing to the public's help
OL,7,Fto do identify who was responsible `
OL,8,Fwere you in the area last night and
OL,9,Fperhaps saw something that seemed
OL,10,Fsuspicious?
OL,12,F" No matter how small the information
OL,13,Fmay seem, it may be crucial to our
OL,14,Finvestigation, and I ask you to
OL,15,Fcontact us or Crimestoppers as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible.
