OL,6,F"This includes any relevant dashcam
OL,7,Ffootage - it is a busy road with
OL,8,Fplenty of vehicles including taxis and
OL,9,Fbuses, which may well have captured
OL,10,Fsomething.
OL,12,F"I would, finally, like to use this
OL,13,Fopportunity to say that we are
OL,14,Fcommitted to identifying those
OL,15,Fresponsible for this reckless
OL,16,Fbehaviour, which could have had
OL,17,Fdevastating consequences for this
OL,18,Ffamily, and ensuring that they face
OL,19,Fjustice."
